
DEUS, qui præ ómnibus Sanctis tuis beátum Jóachim Genitrícis Fílii tui patrem esse voluísti: concéde, quæsumus; ut, cujus festa venerámur, ejus quoque perpétuo patrocínia sentiámus. Per eúmdem Dóminum.
O GOD, who didst choose blessed Joachim, before all thy Saints, to be the father of her who bore thy Son; grant, we beseech thee, that as we celebrate his festival, we may also ever experience his patronage. Through the same.
